ass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n離心力如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f4d4163fc599738c429b294081618939b999ea","tid":198204,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"我5月尾去，都考慮緊，留名先<br />\n但我海洋公園，迪士尼所有機動遊戲都會玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7ff24432d07429b4b300cd5fefbff0ca6d2f73","tid":198204,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我5月尾去，都考慮緊，留名先<br />\n但我海洋公園，迪士尼所有機動遊戲都會玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但台灣六褔村個個真係唔夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66946522abf9aeadcea3dc439225b5bf719f9929","tid":198204,"uid":42175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"因為舊野鎖到好實<br />\n你係同貼到實撚晒<br />\n玩個陣唔會有浪下拋下個種感覺<br />\n所以係無乜離心力<br />\n可以安心上路"},{"pid":"6ba4dba8740750410a599e1404244d93d809cd67","tid":198204,"uid":7835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我5月尾去，都考慮緊，留名先<br />\n但我海洋公園，迪士尼所有機動遊戲都會玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海洋公園嗰d都敢玩咁絕對冇問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22afb8f017d7c8ad3e5ad634d301b41623b49df8","tid":198204,"uid":7835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為舊野鎖到好實<br />\n你係同貼到實撚晒<br />\n玩個陣唔會有浪下拋下個種感覺<br />\n所以係無乜離心力<br />\n可以安心上路</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有你呢句決定豁出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda2117330e888f2537a539b54238a42665333db","tid":198204,"uid":23360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為舊野鎖到好實<br />\n你係同貼到實撚晒<br />\n玩個陣唔會有浪下拋下個種感覺<br />\n所以係無乜離心力<br />\n可以安心上路</blockquote><br />\n無錯 , 其實上到去都無咩野"},{"pid":"17d3c67cb52e4be9a22e4dba5e675fbe6ebf9314","tid":198204,"uid":45747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:39:52.000Z","msg":"倒轉坐驚啲"},{"pid":"39610fec034e89bea21aa654892577c5ec16992b","tid":198204,"uid":4008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"買左翼龍fastpass但最後淆底無玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚大座好撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就咁睇都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bf8ad4e56ff30341528a83fc39694898b3b01d","tid":198204,"uid":49978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:19:16.000Z","msg":"冇料到<br />\n眼鏡撚被迫除眼鏡，玩完好似冇玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8039cd34a08ea518d6e5c048a9dd6c3b6b0023bd","tid":198204,"uid":92307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打有玩過柯南<br />\n小弟遲啲同屋企人去USJ, 我諗住玩埋柯南<br />\n但係我見網上啲意見好兩極 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟淨係學左少少日文, 屋企人就唔識日文<br />\n我淨係知佢地提供個pad有中文揀<br />\n驚屋企人玩得唔開心, 唔想到時玩完俾屋企人插到飛起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下呢到有冇巴打玩過, 可唔可以分享下感想, thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230cbb80f5269b3f8d381c76e2606b19f0a5dee3","tid":198204,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打有玩過柯南<br />\n小弟遲啲同屋企人去USJ, 我諗住玩埋柯南<br />\n但係我見網上啲意見好兩極 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟淨係學左少少日文, 屋企人就唔識日文<br />\n我淨係知佢地提供個pad有中文揀<br />\n驚屋企人玩得唔開心, 唔想到時玩完俾屋企人插到飛起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下呢到有冇巴打玩過, 可唔可以分享下感想, thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n千其唔好<br />\n我今年入院最後悔玩柯南<br />\n晒撚左個幾鍾時間<br />\n本身冇睇柯南<br />\n加上日文又多解迷，想中途放棄又唔知點走<br />\non99咁<br />\n好采買晒pass叫做玩晒其他"},{"pid":"b3651dba982365b7d070fb94577120a6ec76209c","tid":198204,"uid":36755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:12:37.000Z","msg":"今年一月去左<br />\n自己覺得離心力有一個人廿"},{"pid":"983d093120772ed8109ce0a5c0a9ad25eb144dac","tid":198204,"uid":36755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年一月去左<br />\n自己覺得離心力有一個位好勁（唔太玩機動遊戲）<br />\n但係好好玩風景好靚<br />\n唔玩會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"}]}